Signed-off-by: Shang XiaoJing <shangxiaojing@huawei.com>
Reviewed-by: Krzysztof Kozlowski <krzysztof.kozlowski@linaro.org>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20221020030505.15572-1-shangxiaojing@huawei.com
